modDescription:
Find and crash a party to stop a spy set out on a mission to kill every party goer there. Help Leah Martini figure out which attendee is the spy and take them out quietly with a syringe of poison. Choose carefully though. The spy is carrying a bomb ready to detonate at any moment if thereâ€™s a commotion. Killing an innocent party-er will definitely make the spy trigger the bomb!

Requires restart. Requires client to install as well as server.

Tested and works with Alpha 19.4 b7

Recommended to be played single player or multiplayer.

**[Download](https://www.dropbox.com/s/zbsbq59ebmjtskc/TelricsSpyPartyA19.zip?dl=1)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19976-telrics-a19-modlets/).
